Ruger® LCP®









From Backup Firearms for Law Enforcement to Licensed Carry for Personal Protection
The Ruger® LCP® Is the Perfect Choice



Rugged construction with through-hardened steel slide and one-piece, high-performance, glass-filled nylon grip frame.


Compact at just 5.16"13.1 cm long and 3.60"91 mm tall, the LCP® is designed to fit a variety of holsters and provide concealed carry options.


 Checkered grip frame provides a secure and comfortable grip.




 Includes finger grip extension floorplate that can be added to the magazine for comfort and grip.


 Fixed front and rear sights are integral to the slide, while the hammer is recessed within the slide.




 Also includes one 6-round magazine.


 Blued, alloy steel barrel.




Lightweight, Compact and Powerful.




